@startuml SD-07_Scan_Schedule

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName "Arial"
skinparam defaultFontSize 17
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam dpi 300



skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
    FontStyle plain
}
skinparam actor {
    BackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    BorderColor #555555
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}
skinparam sequence {
    ArrowColor #333333
    ArrowThickness 1
    ArrowFontColor #000000
    ArrowFontSize 16
    LifeLineBorderColor #333333
    LifeLineBorderThickness 1
    LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
    GroupBodyBackgroundColor #F8F8F8
    GroupBorderColor #888888
    GroupBorderThickness 1
    GroupHeaderFontColor #000000
    DividerBackgroundColor #E8E8E8
    DividerFontColor #000000
    DividerBorderColor #AAAAAA
    DividerBorderThickness 1
    ParticipantBorderThickness 1
}
skinparam note {
    BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
    BorderColor #999999
    BorderThickness 1
    FontColor #000000
}

actor       "User"         as User
participant "Web\nUI"      as UI
participant "Schedules\nController" as Ctrl
participant "Schedules\nService" as Svc
participant "Scan\nAPI"    as ScanAPI
database    "DB"           as DB

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Create Schedule ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

User -> UI  : Select asset, frequency\nscan type & time of day
UI   -> Ctrl : POST /api/scan-schedules
Ctrl -> Svc : create(orgId, userId, dto)

Svc  -> DB  : findOne(Asset)
DB  --> Svc  : asset
Svc  -> Svc : calculateNextRun(frequency)
Svc  -> DB  : save(ScanSchedule)
DB  --> Svc  : savedSchedule

Svc --> Ctrl : schedule
Ctrl --> UI  : 201 Created
UI  --> User : Toast "Schedule created"

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Scheduled Trigger (Planned) ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

note over Svc, ScanAPI
  [Planned] CRON job runs periodically,
  triggers due scans, updates nextRunAt.
end note

Svc  -> DB  : find(ScanSchedule, due)
DB  --> Svc  : due schedules[]

Svc  -> ScanAPI : POST /api/scans
ScanAPI --> Svc  : 201 Created (scanId)

Svc  -> DB  : update(nextRunAt)
DB  --> Svc  : updated

' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
== Toggle / Delete Schedule ==
' ═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

User -> UI  : Toggle schedule on/off
UI   -> Ctrl : PATCH /api/scan-schedules/:id
Ctrl -> Svc : update(isActive)
Svc  -> DB  : save(schedule)
DB  --> Svc  : updated
Svc --> Ctrl : schedule
Ctrl --> UI  : 200 OK
UI  --> User : Toast "Schedule updated"

@enduml
